page.title: 20CLASS THREE PUTTENHAM SCHOOL
page.content: Nineteen of the twenty-seven children in the top class of{Puttenham Church {of England First School}are leaving at the end of the Summer term 1985. It is a small village school on the slopes of the North Downs and surrounded by green fields.{The Domesday Project}has been completed by - Anthony Dexter,Joanna Staerck, Mark Ferguson, Daniel Thorpe, Rupert Townsend, Claire Coleman, James Hatcher, Virginia Mathisen, Jonathan Kirkpatrick, Sarah Seymour, Rupert Whicker, Clare Mills, Oliver Cox, Kate Hopwood, Robert Hewitson, Roderick Sandys, Benjamin Hart, Andrew Chester, Matthew Poole, Martin Lowe, Douglas White, Christopher Murray, Sam Richardson, James Young, Michael Holdship, Joanna Cleaver, Alexander Gowar. M.E.SAUNDERS.
